Sir Thomas Mansfield Forbes Parkyns, 6th Bt.1

M, #655752, b. 30 April 1853, d. 2 February 1926

Last Edited=24 Jan 2015

Sir Thomas Mansfield Forbes Parkyns, 6th Bt. was born on 30 April 1853.1 He was the son of Sir Thomas George Augustus Parkyns, 5th Bt. and Annie Jennings.1 He married Beatrice Crawford, daughter of Arthur Travers Crawford, on 14 July 1886.1 He died on 2 February 1926 at age 72.1

He was a practising barrister-at-law.1 He succeeded as the 6th Baronet Parkyns, of Bunny, co. Nottingham [E., 1681] on 7 March 1895.1 On his death, his baronetcy became dormant.2

Sylvia Dorothy Parkyns1

F, #655755

Last Edited=24 Jan 2015

Sylvia Dorothy Parkyns is the daughter of Sir Thomas Mansfield Forbes Parkyns, 6th Bt. and Beatrice Crawford.1 She married Allan Gilbert Cram in 1912.1 She and Allan Gilbert Cram were divorced in 1931.1

From 1912, her married name became Cram.1 She lived in 1970 at Santa Barbara, California, U.S.A.1
